{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Now as I say, at this moment, you own nothing else anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "You have now lost your name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "That is the ultimate dehumanization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "You think that is the end of the dehumanization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "There is nothing else now anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Now you're in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And you just hang in there for dear life, literally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my number here is right on my left arm here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's B11291.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is sort of like upside down when you hold-- when I hold it like this, because it has to be like this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to hold the arm this way that when the SS man looked at it, when you had to recite it, that he could easily read along with it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he has it right on there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now by the way, there were about some 20 rows of tattooers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the row that I was, it happened to be that the guy apparently was neat, because I know a fellow here in Saint Paul that has his number on the outside of his arm, very, very crooked and, and uneven.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many people ask me, why do you have that thing yet?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why don't you get rid of it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have no reason to get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's not a big operation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a minor skin graft.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's not a big deal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I don't see any reason for it-- nothing to be ashamed of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So this now, then when this was done, then we were taken into the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And yes, and there the food was there, the bowl of soup and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the guy with his megaphone couldn't, couldn't help but making another remark, saying, look you guys.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
